i say that i got tough skin, i don’t...

“DAYS LIKE THIS” OUT AUGUST 18TH!!! 🥀 
PRE-SAVE IN BIOOO 
I’ve been keeping this a secret for way too long…
after almost two years of practically living in the studio - I was breaking down, breaking up & breaking through. I vomited all my pain, love & extremely honest thoughts in this new music. my best friends & I created something so personal - it’s lowkey a little scary, BUT I can’t wait for you to hear my heart in sonic form. IN TWO WEEKSSSS u will hear DAYS. LIKE. THISSSSS.
Ahhhhh tell ur friends, PRESAVE & I just love u

my best friend is now an angel. 🪽 so grateful to grow up with you. I met u when I was 7 & knew you were the one, I bought my first songwriting notebook at petsmart & wrote one of my first songs about you 🥹 (on the last slide) 
you were my rock through my tweens, teens & my early twenties. there’s sooo many memories of you from stealing our breakfast every morning before school to finding you sitting on the couch listening to me whenever I play piano. so grateful for your unconditional love for 14 years 🫶🏻 this isn’t a goodbye because I feel your energy around me all the time. I love you forever Cooper. 
visit me in my dreams tonight 🤍
